snippet.title: Ship Builder - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
This is not another building simulator! Ship Builder is a breath of fresh air in the genre. Create your ships from scratch, get the wood and raw materials needed to make each of the planks and structural elements. Add the game to your wishlist today!

STEAM PAGE: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1051440/
DISCORD: https://discord.gg/md6ezrQrqe
TWITTER: https://twitter.com/ShipBuilderGame
FACEBOOK: https://www.facebook.com/shipbuilderthegame
INSTAGRAM: https://www.instagram.com/ship_builder_the_game/
